description:
Getaround - Rent a car from someone nearby

"Great way to rent on the go!" 
"Essential companion to a great service." 
"Works flawlessly." 

Share your car and earn thousands a year. Rent anything from a Tesla to a Prius.
Insurance included. FREE to join & no annual fees! Login with Facebook.

PRESS QUOTES
• "The Airbnb for cars" - TechCrunch 
• "This is a holy smokes moment!" - Chris Sacca, TechCrunch judge and angel Investor
• “Getaround Will Make Every Car A Rental Car.” - Fast Company 
• "The law is on our side. (Because we helped write it)." - Inc Magazine (cover)
• "Rent a Tesla Roadster for $25/hr." - GOOD
• “We love the idea.” - Treehugger 

FEATURES
• Astonishingly LOW PRICES on a great variety of cars in your neighborhood.
• FREE SIGNUP and no annual fees. INSURANCE INCLUDED. 
• FAST AND EASY. No paperwork, lines, hidden fees or membership card. 
• SAFE and TRUSTED community with driver screening and rating system.
• 24/7 customer happiness line and roadside assistance.
• Good for the ENVIRONMENT and your COMMUNITY.

SUPPORTED CITIES (more launching soon)
• San Francisco (Bay Area)
• Chicago
• Austin
• Portland
• San Diego
